      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, presenting in collector-grade condition with impeccable mechanical provenance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring a high-pressure double VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and razor-sharp throttle response across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers short, tactile throws, channeling power through a variable M-differential lock with zero lash. The chassis remains remarkably stiff, with the critical rear subframe mounting points proactively reinforced for long-term structural integrity. Suspension kinematics are factory-correct, utilizing aluminum control arms and fresh bushings to preserve the legendary steering feedback and turn-in precision. Finished in a deep, swirl-free gloss with an interior devoid of bolster wear or UV degradation, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically pure, turn-key masterpiece.",
